<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Support the Site - OWCS Tipping</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/global.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/layout.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/components.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/interactive.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/match-cards.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pages/info.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="page-hero support-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Support OWCS Tipping</h1>
        <p class="support-intro">
          I built OWCS Tipping as a fun fan project for people who love following the scene as much as I do.
          If you've enjoyed using the site and want to help keep it running, you can support it here.
        </p>
        <p class="support-subtext">
          No pressure at all, just being here and using the site already means a lot.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="container info-layout">

        <div class="info-card support-highlight">
          <h2>Why support helps</h2>
          <p>
            Support helps cover hosting, the domain, maintenance, and future improvements for the site.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every donation is genuinely appreciated and helps keep the project going.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>A quick note</h2>
          <p>
            Donations do not provide gameplay advantages, bonus credits, better odds, or leaderboard benefits.
          </p>
          <p>
            The tipping system always stays completely fair and separate.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card support-card">
          <h2>Choose an amount</h2>
          <p class="support-card-text">
            If you'd like to chip in, here are a few simple options:
          </p>

          <div class="info-card">
            <h2>VIP Supporter Badge</h2>

            <p>
              Anyone who supports the site can receive an exclusive cosmetic
              <strong>VIP badge</strong> displayed across the website beside their username.
            </p>

            <p>
              When donating, include your OWCS Tipping username or account email in the payment details
              so the badge can be applied to your account.
            </p>

            <p>
              The VIP badge is purely cosmetic and does not provide any gameplay or leaderboard advantage.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="support-buttons">
            <a class="support-btn" href="https://buy.stripe.com/00wfZabZC0KBdGc0EQ6g804" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="support-amount">$5 AUD</span>
              <span class="support-label">Buy me a coffee</span>
            </a>

            <a class="support-btn" href="https://buy.stripe.com/5kQ28k2p278Z45C4V66g805" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="support-amount">$10 AUD</span>
              <span class="support-label">Help with hosting</span>
            </a>

            <a class="support-btn" href="https://buy.stripe.com/4gMaEQaVyfFv45C0EQ6g806" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="support-amount">$20 AUD</span>
              <span class="support-label">Support development</span>
            </a>

            <a class="support-btn" href="https://buy.stripe.com/dRmfZa3t6ctj9pW1IU6g807" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="support-amount">$50 AUD</span>
              <span class="support-label">Massive legend</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <p class="support-thankyou">
            Seriously, thank you — support like this helps make it worth continuing to build and improve the site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>Transparency</h2>
          <p>
            OWCS Tipping is an independent fan-made project and is not affiliated with or endorsed by OWCS or Blizzard.
          </p>
          <p>
            Any support goes toward the site itself and is not tied to tipping credits, match outcomes,
            or real-money wagering of any kind.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>